            . I am the constable. I was sent for on the Monday night: I searched the prisoner, and found this parcel of paste stones in his pocket, (Producing a parcel.)</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. These look like mine: I have a great many such; but the prisoner owned they were mine, and that he had taken them.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence.</p>
